{
  "_purpose": "DISCRIMINATOR (2026-07-05): 2D-P2 on TRIANGLES at the 3D cell (Re=1,Da=1,alpha=0.5). Tests whether the P2 'converged-but-wrong' instability is SIMPLEX-specific (would reproduce here in 2D) or genuinely 3D-only. The sibling phase1_quad_k2.json (same harness/MMS, QUAD) is known-optimal O(h^3) — the control. ASGS-only, the cleanest converges-but-wrong lens.",
